author: ActionMen
title: Diosproc
text: It's the time, it's gone, it's time, it's gone

author: ActionMen
title: Mugna Latin
text: Te he encontrado in un momento

negra como la felonia

you're the hardest stone
but it was so easy to broke you
maravillosa y peligrosa, bruta si pero preziosa
tu encendes los suonos
ponendo las manos asasinas
sinas
come mi mierda
come mi excrementos
morde mi escroto hasta sangrar
you were my hope, I had the heart so dry and hungry
come in my hand alessandra diamond, diamond
like the rock
